.25 billon),France's body\", \"from\": 5835, \"to\": 5862}, {\"ngram\": \"public funds\", \"from\": 5876, \"to\": 5888}, {\"ngram\": \"its most recent study\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5918}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Security remains a challenge for the city repeatedly hit by deadly extremist violence.\", \"from\": 5929, \"to\": 6015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Security\", \"from\": 5929, \"to\": 5937}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 5946, \"to\": 5957}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 5962, \"to\": 5970}, {\"ngram\": \"deadly extremist violence\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 6014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government downsized ambitions to have 600,000 people lining the River Seine for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 6016, \"to\": 6122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6085, \"end\": 6096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 6016, \"to\": 6030}, {\"ngram\": \"ambitions\", \"from\": 6041, \"to\": 6050}, {\"ngram\": \"600,000 people\", \"from\": 6059, \"to\": 6073}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6101, \"to\": 6121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citing the risk of attacks, it shelved a promise that anyone could apply for hundreds of thousands of free tickets.\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 6130, \"to\": 6138}, {\"ngram\": \"attacks\", \"from\": 6142, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"a promise\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6171}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 6177, \"to\": 6183}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds of thousands\", \"from\": 6200, \"to\": 6221}, {\"ngram\": \"free tickets\", \"from\": 6225, \"to\": 6237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the 326,000 spectators will either be paying ticket-holders or have been invited.\", \"from\": 6239, \"to\": 6329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 326,000 spectators\", \"from\": 6248, \"to\": 6270}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket-holders\", \"from\": 6293, \"to\": 6307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Privacy advocates are critical of video surveillance technology being deployed to spot security threats.\", \"from\": 6331, \"to\": 6435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Privacy advocates\", \"from\": 6331, \"to\": 6348}, {\"ngram\": \"video surveillance technology\", \"from\": 6365, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"security threats\", \"from\": 6418, \"to\": 6434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campaigners for the homeless are concerned that they will be swept off streets.\", \"from\": 6436, \"to\": 6515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Campaigners\", \"from\": 6436, \"to\": 6447}, {\"ngram\": \"streets\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many Parisians plan to leave, to avoid the disruptions or to rent their homes to the expected 15 million visitors.\", \"from\": 6516, \"to\": 6630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many Parisians\", \"from\": 6516, \"to\": 6530}, {\"ngram\": \"the disruptions\", \"from\": 6555, \"to\": 6570}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 6582, \"to\": 6593}, {\"ngram\": \"the expected 15 million visitors\", \"from\": 6597, \"to\": 6629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With trade unions pushing for Olympic bonuses, strikes are also possible.\", \"from\": 6631, \"to\": 6704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trade unions\", \"from\": 6636, \"to\": 6648}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bonuses\", \"from\": 6661, \"to\": 6676}, {\"ngram\": \"strikes\", \"from\": 6678, \"to\": 6685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And all this against an inflammable backdrop of geopolitical crises including but not limited to the Israel-Hamas war and Russia's invasion of Ukraine.\", \"from\": 6706, \"to\": 6857, \"entities\": [{\"beg